{"tid":2145708,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「去中國化」再升級  特朗普簽行政命令 禁與TikTok微信交易","createTime":"2020-08-08T07:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T07:45:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3b0d67b6e407ea32d1ef8354e24e77fd9278c1","tid":2145708,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:36:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200808/FADJZSYFM5S6IS2EUASQ52SKXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200808%2FFADJZSYFM5S6IS2EUASQ52SKXE%2F&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDDnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=65f8360b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200808%2FFADJZSYFM5S6IS2EUASQ52SKXE%2F&h=5484541e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200808/FADJZSYFM5S6IS2EUASQ52SKXE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「去中國化」再升級 <br />\n特朗普簽行政命令 禁與TikTok微信交易<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普繼續「去中國化」，昨簽署行政命令禁止所有國民與社交分享網站TikTok母公司字節跳動，以及微信（WeChat）母公司騰訊進行交易，45天後生效。他斥責中國公司的應用程式持續威脅美國的國家安全、外交政策和經濟。TikTok母公司字節跳動稱，對行政命令感震驚，未來可能訴諸法庭。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美不准公僕手機用TikTok<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。旅美學者、原美國律師協會法治項目中國主任虞平分析指：「微信提供服務是違法，運營商跟微信合作也是違法，從這個意義上來說是全面禁止。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rcOTB-ZSHVqtLDkW-_DBPevnqe4=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2JQJVD2BDAFDFHDDRFTQODVSWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrcOTB-ZSHVqtLDkW-_DBPevnqe4%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2JQJVD2BDAFDFHDDRFTQODVSWI.jpg&h=a6348b33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTikTok若不能在限期內賣給美國公司，將被禁在美營運。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n45日後可要求程式下架<br />\n<br />\nCNN則稱美國可要求TikTok及微信在45日後，於Google的Play商店及蘋果的App store 下架。不少中國用戶向外媒稱，擔心與美國使用WeChat 的朋友失去聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在兩份行政命令同樣指出TikTok及微信有同一問題：「自動從用戶方面捕獲大量訊息，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n針對微信的行政命令中，特朗普引述去年3月，有研究人員發現中國的微信數據庫有數十億條訊息，當中不止來自中國用戶，亦包。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nTikTok母公司字節跳動8月7日發表聲明回應，表示對美國總統的行政命令感。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北京警告日不准禁TikTok<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。當地傳媒曾經報道，一群日本執政自民黨國會議員已決定推動立法禁TikTok，因擔心用戶資料恐落入中國政府手裏；但路透社報道，日本政府未表示過考慮禁止TikTok。<br />\n<br />\n白宮網站/彭博社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fj2YGCbQPODtf6PwhM7qzeYLK80=/190x529/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5QCL2LUYZ4ON62MJ5XIBFZYTNE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFj2YGCbQPODtf6PwhM7qzeYLK80%3D%2F190x529%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5QCL2LUYZ4ON62MJ5XIBFZYTNE.gif&h=b35a9a1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4d6ea9ce39fafbc9a4b5b01189c2eff8684be15","tid":2145708,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"腥港人 藍絲 支那留學生 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f20cb71bc4f9e83531cd0444a7fb00f580805e","tid":2145708,"uid":133383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:44:38.000Z","msg":"逐步刺向敵人要害<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f55e0cee4527fe26dfd7b623a0eadd8316de323","tid":2145708,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:44:45.000Z","msg":"wechat冇得pay啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38ae8f65823f64bdaa1842ddaa9e2f835fd5470","tid":2145708,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" 